summary: Example test for koji.build artifact provider
description: |
    Demonstrates how to use the koji.build artifact provider.

    The koji.build provider fetches RPM packages from Koji build system
    using build IDs.

    Example usage:
        prepare:
          - how: artifact
            provide:
              - koji.build:2625600

    This test shows:
    - How to get a build ID from koji
    - How to use --provide koji.build:<build_id>
    - How to verify the package is installed from the artifact repository
tag+:
  - provision-only
  - provision-container
adjust:
  - when: distro != fedora
    enabled: false
    because: Koji provider currently only supports Fedora packages
